    "headline": "Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) Misses Q4 CY2025 Sales Expectations",
    "summary": "Enterprise technology company Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE:HPE) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, but sales rose 18.4% year on year to $9.30 billion. On the other hand, next quarter’s outlook exceeded expectations with revenue guided to $9.8 billion at the midpoint, or 2.8% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.65 per share was 10.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
